  <description type="morphology">Plants to 16 cm. Stems reddish, distinctly visible through wet leaves. Stem leaves moderately concave, 0.8–1.5 mm wide; apex often recurved; alar cells few, orange-brown, quadrate to oblong, slightly enlarged, 18–40 × 12–28 µm; medial laminal cells 50–100 × 6–9 µm; apical cells obviously shorter. Branch leaves concave, 0.8–1.9 × 0.3–0.8 mm. Seta 1.5–4.3 cm. Capsule ellipsoid, 1.5–2.5 mm.</description>
